title: Invasive Species
itunes:title: Invasive Species
description:
Good evening and welcome to Nighty Night with Rabia Chaudry: Bedtime Stories To Keep You Awake.  Tonight's tale is about a man who, let's just say, is going through a bit of a transition in his life.  Please enjoy Invasive Species. 

Tonight's tale was written by Travis Madden.
